import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'
import ProducteGallery from './ProducteGallery'
import ProducteText from './ProducteText'


const ProducteDetalis = () => {
  return (
   <Container>
       <Row>
        <Col sm='4' md='6'>
        <ProducteGallery/>
   
        </Col>
        <Col sm='8'>
        <ProducteText/>
        </Col>
      </Row>
   </Container>
  )
}

export default ProducteDetalis
